@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rosofb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.19)))
    v1 = v2
    v1 = 1.00
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.30) - (v0 + 0.78 + v2 + 0.92)) - v0)
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.10 / tmp + 0.78) + tmp))
    tmp = (0.89 - 0.51)
    v2 = v1
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
